    "A device wants to pair with **%@**.\nAllow this device to connect?" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ein Gerät möchte sich mit **%@** koppeln.\nDieses Gerät verbinden lassen?"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "有设备想要与 **%@** 配对。\n允许此设备连接吗？"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A different dino for every job. Your memories stick around, ready when you need them." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Für jede Aufgabe ein anderer Dino. Deine Erinnerungen bleiben erhalten, bereit, wenn du sie brauchst."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "每项工作都有不同的小恐龙。你的记忆会一直保留，需要时随时可用。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A microphone button will appear in the chat input when voice is ready" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Eine Mikrofon-Schaltfläche erscheint in der Chat-Eingabe, wenn Stimme bereit ist"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "当语音准备好时，麦克风按钮将出现在聊天输入中"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A quick tour" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Eine kurze Tour"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "快速浏览"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A safety net for your dino" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ein Sicherheitsnetz für deinen Dino"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "为你的小恐龙提供的安全网"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A short code that proves what you make is really yours." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ein kurzer Code, der beweist, dass das, was du erstellst, wirklich dir gehört."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "一段简短的代码，用于证明你创建的内容确实属于你。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A short code that proves what you make is really yours. We back it up in iCloud Keychain so it follows you across your Apple devices." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ein kurzer Code, der beweist, dass das, was du erstellst, wirklich dir gehört. Wir sichern ihn im iCloud-Schlüsselbund, damit er dich über deine Apple-Geräte hinweg begleitet."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "一段简短的代码，用于证明你创建的内容确实属于你。我们会将其备份到 iCloud 钥匙串中，以便它在你的各台 Apple 设备间同步。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A stalled provider or dropped connection can hang a request indefinitely. You'll have to stop it manually" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ein hängender Anbieter oder eine abgebrochene Verbindung kann eine Anfrage unbegrenzt blockieren. Du musst sie manuell stoppen"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "停滞的提供方或断开的连接可能使请求无限期挂起。你需要手动停止它"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "About 2.8 GB. The detection model runs entirely on your Mac — no third-party traffic for detection." : {
      "comment" : "Footnote text in the PrivacyInstallHero, describing the size and privacy of the model.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Etwa 2,8 GB. Das Erkennungsmodell läuft vollständig auf deinem Mac – kein Drittanbieter-Datenverkehr für die Erkennung."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "约 2.8 GB。检测模型完全在你的 Mac 上运行——检测过程没有任何第三方流量。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
