    "Pace incoming tokens at a steady rate so streaming looks like a typewriter across all providers. Disable to render tokens as soon as they arrive — useful with very fast remote providers that you'd rather see complete instantly." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Pace incoming tokens at a steady rate so streaming looks like a typewriter across all providers. Disable to render tokens as soon as they arrive — useful with very fast remote providers that you'd rather see complete instantly."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "让传入的 token 以稳定的速率逐字出现，这样无论哪个远程提供商，流式输出都像打字机一样连贯。禁用此功能后，token 会在到达时立即渲染 — 这对于您希望立即完成的非常快速的远程提供者很有用。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
